de.fu_berlin.maniac.network_manager

Class NodePair

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fu_berlin.maniac.network_manager.NodePair

  • public class NodePair
extends java.lang.Object
    Node pairs represent information about the whole mesh network. Single pairs show known relations between nodes in the network. For more information please refer to the OLSRd documentation, since this is just our representation of the network info the olsr daemon spits out with the txtinfo plugin
    Author:
    ponken
